descriptionHtml:
Ok im am giving away a free copy of Morrowind all you have to do to try and win it is post a comment about my mods and ill pick the best review,



I am writing books on the daedric princes,as of now i have the books of Molag bal,Mehrunes dagon,and Sheogorath and yes there is a fully voiced quest remember that the books to start the quest are at the throat of the world,plus you get to fight all of the daedric princes

ENDORSE ME PLEASE AND JOIN THE DAKON ARMY

Also if you have any questions please ask and i give permission to make a video about my mod.
(PART 2)
i added the books of Malacath,Clavicus vile,and Jyggalag.
all the new and old books can be found at the throat of the world
